Take a deep breath.

00:40:29.532 --> 00:40:30.562
Now, hold it.

00:40:34.062 --> 00:40:36.432
You're taking this test of your own free will, correct?

00:40:37.572 --> 00:40:39.872
A living donor liver transplant is the best option, you see.

00:40:41.112 --> 00:40:43.612
Well, just because you're siblings doesn't guarantee a match,

00:40:44.212 --> 00:40:45.612
so don't get your hopes up too high.

00:40:48.082 --> 00:40:51.682
- Why isn't Eun Oh here today? - Well...

00:40:51.982 --> 00:40:55.192
It's a personal matter, so it's not really my place to say.

00:40:55.652 --> 00:40:56.652
Su Jeong.

00:40:56.722 --> 00:40:59.062
I really can't. You should ask Eun Oh yourself.

00:40:59.162 --> 00:41:02.332
She's never missed a day of school. That's why I'm asking.

00:41:05.332 --> 00:41:06.332
All right, fine.

00:41:09.972 --> 00:41:11.972
It's so obvious he likes Eun Oh.

