(Wow, I can't believe this outfit is 68 years old.)

00:41:15.472 --> 00:41:16.512
(Bini, gorgeous colours. I love the vibe.)

00:41:16.572 --> 00:41:18.442
(- I'd totally buy this outfit. - Grandma looks just like a model.)

00:41:18.512 --> 00:41:19.512
(She's so elegant.)

