00:44:23.492 --> 00:44:26.202
I can't stand seeing my dad live all by himself anymore.

00:44:30.232 --> 00:44:31.232
Dad...

00:44:32.372 --> 00:44:34.302
He's been on antidepressants.

00:44:35.342 --> 00:44:37.412
Why didn't you tell me that?

00:44:37.772 --> 00:44:39.942
You should have told me this. Come on.

00:44:40.542 --> 00:44:42.482
Is this because I'm not making enough money right now?

00:44:42.812 --> 00:44:43.812
Da Jeong.

00:44:45.782 --> 00:44:48.552
Did my words go in one ear and out the other?

00:44:49.292 --> 00:44:51.892
I told you he could come live with us.

00:44:52.192 --> 00:44:55.732
What? Mother, you said he could live with us?

00:44:55.832 --> 00:44:59.932
Yes. Su Bin and I can share a room, and he can have mine.

00:45:01.062 --> 00:45:02.402
No, I couldn't ask you to do that.

00:45:02.672 --> 00:45:04.072
Why not? Of course, we can do it.

00:45:04.372 --> 00:45:07.002
We can just kick out either Ji Wan or Ji Hyuk.

00:45:07.242 --> 00:45:09.672
Mother offered to let your father move in, right?

00:45:10.672 --> 00:45:13.082
But still, there's Gyeong Hun.

00:45:13.882 --> 00:45:16.712
You wrote that text to your brother,

00:45:17.012 --> 00:45:18.352
but you couldn't hit send, could you?

00:45:19.052 --> 00:45:20.922
You were afraid he'd say no, weren't you?

00:45:23.392 --> 00:45:24.392
Mother.

00:45:25.762 --> 00:45:28.162
Are you really sure you'd be okay with my father living here?

00:45:30.632 --> 00:45:31.702
And you're really okay with this?

00:45:32.262 --> 00:45:34.062
- Of course! - Of course! Honestly...

00:45:38.302 --> 00:45:40.442
- Honey, it's Gyeong Hun. - Answer it.

00:45:42.842 --> 00:45:45.182
Hello? Gyeong Hun?

00:45:45.612 --> 00:45:47.982
Hey. Sorry it took me so long to call back.

00:45:48.452 --> 00:45:51.882
Yes. Isn't it like 1am in Seattle now?

00:45:52.522 --> 00:45:54.452
We moved today. We just finished unpacking.

00:45:55.592 --> 00:45:58.662
- You moved? - Yes, into a four-bedroom place.

00:45:59.522 --> 00:46:00.522
So Dad can come and live with us.

00:46:01.692 --> 00:46:02.992
You want Dad to live with you?

00:46:13.572 --> 00:46:15.312
Apparently, my sister-in-law suggested it first.

00:46:16.072 --> 00:46:18.342
Her mother passed away at the beginning of the year.

00:46:19.882 --> 00:46:22.612
So she told him he'd regret it for the rest of his life...

00:46:23.412 --> 00:46:24.852
if he didn't ask our father to come live with them.

00:46:26.152 --> 00:46:28.152
Still, that means leaving the country.

00:46:28.792 --> 00:46:30.492
Do you think your father will be happy with that?

00:46:31.522 --> 00:46:34.622
- He'll be thrilled. - Da Jeong!

00:46:35.332 --> 00:46:36.391
- Sang Cheol! - Father.

00:46:36.392 --> 00:46:38.302
- My goodness. - Oh, Ok Rye.

00:46:40.502 --> 00:46:44.332
My Gyeong Hun asked me to come.

00:46:45.142 --> 00:46:46.302
He wants me to live with him.

00:46:47.372 --> 00:46:49.412
- "Ok Rye?" - "Ok Rye?"

00:46:56.482 --> 00:46:59.782
Wait, how did they become friends just by being neighbours?

00:47:00.882 --> 00:47:02.692
You heard him. He said he had no friends left.

00:47:03.322 --> 00:47:06.762
Wow, I've never seen your father look so happy.

00:47:07.792 --> 00:47:09.262
He must have been so lonely.

00:47:13.002 --> 00:47:14.532
I'm sorry, honey. Okay?

00:47:16.802 --> 00:47:19.041
What about Mother once my dad leaves?

00:47:19.042 --> 00:47:20.242
She'll feel so empty.

00:47:22.742 --> 00:47:23.742
Kim Da Jeong.

00:47:25.012 --> 00:47:26.012
Stay with me for a long time.

00:47:26.912 --> 00:47:29.252
For a long time? How long?

00:47:30.312 --> 00:47:32.922
At this rate, we probably have at least another 20 years together.

00:47:33.952 --> 00:47:38.152
No, maybe 30, looking at our parents.

00:47:38.922 --> 00:47:39.922
Thirty years?

00:47:40.892 --> 00:47:42.592
Oh, you're right.

00:47:43.492 --> 00:47:44.492
Don't worry.

00:47:45.232 --> 00:47:47.762
I won't burden you with being the sole provider until then.

00:47:48.232 --> 00:47:49.472
I'll be right there with you.

00:47:50.272 --> 00:47:51.432
Don't be ridiculous.

00:47:51.942 --> 00:47:54.142
I'll be the one providing for you until the day I die. Honestly...

00:47:56.542 --> 00:47:58.482
This is exactly why I married you.

00:48:06.622 --> 00:48:07.852
Mom, Gang Oh.

00:48:08.122 --> 00:48:10.292
- So how was it today? - It felt like it was a shoo-in.

00:48:10.852 --> 00:48:12.422
I think Mom's galbi is going to be a new menu item.

00:48:12.992 --> 00:48:13.992
Wow, really?

00:48:14.962 --> 00:48:18.232
My gosh. You really worked hard, Mom.

00:48:19.162 --> 00:48:20.162
Goodness.

00:48:21.502 --> 00:48:22.532
Hey, I'm exhausted.

00:48:23.072 --> 00:48:24.072
I'm heading to bed.

00:48:30.342 --> 00:48:31.342
Gang Oh.

00:48:31.842 --> 00:48:34.282
Did something happen to upset Mom today?

00:48:34.612 --> 00:48:37.212
No, I don't think so. She was proud of the great response.

00:48:38.422 --> 00:48:40.482
So is she just really exhausted then?

00:48:41.122 --> 00:48:43.622
Of course, she is. Our mom is a huge introvert,

00:48:43.692 --> 00:48:44.962
and she had to do a demo at corporate HQ.

00:48:47.822 --> 00:48:48.832
Yes, that makes sense.

00:48:55.032 --> 00:48:56.102
That little brat.

00:48:58.102 --> 00:48:59.642
I can't believe she didn't say anything.

00:49:05.042 --> 00:49:06.042
My gosh.

00:49:13.852 --> 00:49:16.522
(Bid Envelope)

00:49:18.922 --> 00:49:21.122
- Your submission is complete. - Okay.

00:49:21.792 --> 00:49:23.532
(Bidder: Lee Ji Hyuk)

00:49:29.572 --> 00:49:31.272
- Shall we go? - Yes.

00:49:32.502 --> 00:49:35.812
Wait, Mr. Lee, you're here for the final bidding?

00:49:36.112 --> 00:49:37.112
Yes.

00:49:42.182 --> 00:49:43.182
For crying out loud.

00:49:44.582 --> 00:49:45.582
This is ridiculous.

00:49:49.552 --> 00:49:51.592
Thank you for seeing this through with me.

00:49:52.592 --> 00:49:54.362
Regardless of the outcome, we've learned a lot from this too.

00:49:55.062 --> 00:49:56.762
Your fighting spirit and tenacity...

00:49:57.032 --> 00:49:58.432
It's something we never would have dreamed of.

00:49:59.102 --> 00:50:01.302
If that's how it seemed, it's all thanks to my father.

00:50:01.772 --> 00:50:05.372
- Pardon? - He told me to go for it.

00:50:06.142 --> 00:50:07.272
Whether it worked out or not,

00:50:07.702 --> 00:50:10.012
I figured it'd be better than regretting not trying.

00:50:10.872 --> 00:50:11.882
I see.

00:50:12.582 --> 00:50:15.182
You really left it all on the table. So how do you feel?

00:50:16.112 --> 00:50:17.112
Relieved.

00:50:18.112 --> 00:50:20.322
I know the feeling. I feel relieved myself.

00:50:21.052 --> 00:50:22.052
What?

00:50:23.252 --> 00:50:25.092
(Yoon Tae Sik Vice President, AP Group)

00:50:27.992 --> 00:50:28.992
Hello, this is Lee Ji Hyuk.

00:50:29.062 --> 00:50:31.832
Mr. Lee. The chairman wants to see you now.

00:50:32.232 --> 00:50:35.771
- Pardon? - I'll text you the contract needs.

00:50:35.772 --> 00:50:36.872
Prepare them and come.

00:50:38.272 --> 00:50:39.972
What do you mean by that?

00:50:41.102 --> 00:50:43.472
He's handing the company to you, Mr. Lee.

00:50:45.112 --> 00:50:46.112
What?

00:51:24.934 --> 00:51:27.252
(Exclusive Negotiation Agreement)

00:51:27.652 --> 00:51:31.292
What are you staring at so dreamily? Weren't you expecting this at all?

00:51:33.092 --> 00:51:34.862
You're a very convincing actor, Mr. Chairman.

00:51:35.532 --> 00:51:37.232
You were just acting that day, weren't you?

00:51:37.592 --> 00:51:40.002
I made my decision the day you came to see me.

00:51:41.162 --> 00:51:44.102
I want to hand my company over to someone who will grow it well.

00:51:44.772 --> 00:51:48.242
What would I do with all that money from the sale at my age, anyway?

00:51:49.412 --> 00:51:50.412
But...

00:51:51.512 --> 00:51:52.912
I needed to be sure.

00:51:54.442 --> 00:51:57.482
Whether you had just ambition, or the grit to back it up too.

00:51:59.252 --> 00:52:00.882
The kind of man who finishes what he starts...

00:52:01.582 --> 00:52:05.052
would make it to the final bid, so I waited to see.

00:52:06.622 --> 00:52:08.192
Thank you for believing in me.

00:52:08.762 --> 00:52:09.862
I won't let you down.

00:52:14.362 --> 00:52:16.002
Please take good care of this company.

00:52:28.412 --> 00:52:29.952
This is our company logo.

00:52:30.712 --> 00:52:33.482
I had this made once I made up my mind.

00:52:34.022 --> 00:52:35.452
To help me let go of the company.

00:52:37.422 --> 00:52:39.522
I wanted to give it to the new owner as a gift.

00:52:42.962 --> 00:52:43.962
Now,

00:52:44.892 --> 00:52:46.102
it's not my company anymore.

00:52:57.542 --> 00:52:59.212
This is gorgeous.

00:53:02.852 --> 00:53:04.852
The height of the sink...

00:53:05.782 --> 00:53:06.782
